headline: 3 Profitable Stocks Walking a Fine Line
summary: While profitability is essential, it doesn’t guarantee long-term success. Some companies that rest on their margins will lose ground as competition intensifies - as Jeff Bezos said, "Your margin is my opportunity".

headline: Tapestry, Inc. to Host FY25 Third Quarter Earnings Call
summary: NEW YORK, April 24, 2025--On Thursday, May 8, 2025 at 8:00 a.m. (ET), Tapestry, Inc. (NYSE: TPR) will hold a conference call to discuss the Company’s fiscal 2025 third quarter results which will be reported via press release earlier that morning.
